00:12:40,940 --> 00:12:42,780
clearly a kind and reasonable girl.

288
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:45,220
She's so young, yet unable to see.

289
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:48,580
If we can cure her eyes,

290
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,300
that'd be a good deed.

291
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,300
Don't worry.

292
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,180
It's just three days, okay?

293
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:57,300
Fine.

294
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:59,100
I'll pick you up in three days.

295
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:03,060
Your Highness,

296
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:06,620
may I ask if the mole
near the Princess's eye

297
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,460
was there since birth,

298
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:10,020
or if it appeared

299
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,040
after she lost her sight?

300
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:12,740
Fuqing was born

301
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:14,820
without a mole near her eye.

302
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:16,800
Now that you mention it,

303
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:18,540
that mole

304
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:19,900
only appeared

305
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:20,980
after she became blind.

306
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:24,980
Was its color light

307
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,500
at first,

308
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:29,540
but it deepened over the years?

309
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,620
Yes.

310
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:33,900
But isn't that how all moles are?

311
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:35,940
That's why

312
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:38,220
a small mole like that

313
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:41,260
wouldn't raise suspicion.

314
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,020
Everyone, leave us.

315
00:14:00,260 --> 00:14:01,260
What do you mean?

316
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,940
Is Fuqing's mole

317
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:05,020
related to her blindness?

318
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:07,300
I once read in an ancient text

319
00:14:07,860 --> 00:14:08,980
about a Mang Worm

320
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,700
that can reside in people's eyes,

321
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,300
blocking their meridians

322
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:13,420
and sealing their vision,

323
00:14:13,420 --> 00:14:14,900
plunging them into eternal darkness.

324
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:16,420
The "mole" near the Princess's eye

325
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:17,460
isn't a mole.

326
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:19,660
It's a worm cyst.

327
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:20,900
A worm cyst?

328
00:14:23,020 --> 00:14:24,140
So, my daughter's blindness

329
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,540
wasn't caused

330
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,340
by the light of the sky lanterns?

331
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:28,700
Did the Mang Worm

332
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,580
reside in Fuqing's eye

333
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:31,620
on its own?

334
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:34,140
These worms require careful cultivation

335
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,140
to survive inside a human eye.

336
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:38,300
Are you saying

337
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:40,100
someone deliberately tried

338
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,540
to blind Fuqing?

339
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:42,980
Yes.

340
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:51,860
Since the day I entered the Palace,

341
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:55,300
I've never envied nor resented anyone.

342
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,380
I've never made enemies
among the consorts.

343
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:01,740
I've never scolded the maids

344
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:05,820
and eunuchs in my service harshly.

345
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:09,340
I have done everything I could.

346
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:13,260
Why would someone

347
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,700
still want to harm my child?

348
00:15:18,980 --> 00:15:21,140
She's merely a Princess,

349
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:23,180
unable to fight for power or the throne.

350
00:15:24,020 --> 00:15:26,820
Who would be so cruel?

351
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:28,500
Your Highness,

352
00:15:28,940 --> 00:15:30,220
we must find

353
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,140
the culprit.

354
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:32,460
Perhaps if we do,

355
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:34,180
the Princess's sight

356
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:35,980
may be restored.

357
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:43,220
Your Highness,

358
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,700
Jiang Si went to visit
Consort Xian yesterday

359
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:46,940
and was punished.

360
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:48,940
Yet today, she went to visit

361
00:15:48,940 --> 00:15:50,780
the Empress with Prince Yan

362
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:53,700
and stayed to learn palace etiquette.

363
00:15:54,940 --> 00:15:56,860
She certainly knows how to adapt.

364
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,420
Realizing that Consort Xian
won't protect her,

365
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:01,480
she's now trying to gain favor
with the Empress.

366
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:02,860
Unfortunately,

367
00:16:03,180 --> 00:16:04,580
she has chosen the wrong patron.

368
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:09,940
After returning to the Palace,

369
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:13,380
tell the Nanwu woman
to clean up her tracks asap.

370
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:14,940
Yes.

371
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:17,180
Your Highness, I'd like to ask

372
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:20,060
if all your personal maids

373
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:22,040
moved to Changning Palace with you

374
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:24,100
before you were made Empress.

375
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:29,220
Are you suggesting

376
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:31,700
that the one who placed the worm

377
00:16:32,180 --> 00:16:33,900
is an old servant of mine?

378
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:37,780
The Mang Worm is difficult
to survive in the eye.

379
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:39,420
It requires careful nurturing

380
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:40,500
over time.

381
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:42,140
Princess Fuqing

382
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:43,620
fell ill shortly

383
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:44,840
before you became the Empress.

384
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:46,020
So, I suspect

385
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,540
this person must have moved

386
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:48,680
to Changning Palace as well.

387
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:51,940
At that time,

388
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,180
no one in the harem

389
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:55,820
could have predicted

390
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,500
that I'd become the Empress.

391
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:59,860
I have no sons.

392
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:01,660
My family has no power.

393
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:04,260
His Majesty never favored me.

394
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:08,420
I had only five personal maids.

395
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:10,980
Among them,

396
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:13,900
only Ms. Hua and Ms. Duo remain.

397
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:16,000
- Could it be...?
- Please don't be anxious.

398
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,660
This is just my conjecture.

399
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:19,820
It could never be them.

400
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:22,380
Ms. Hua

401
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:25,140
practically raised Fuqing.

402
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:27,300
She cherishes her like her own eyes.

403
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:30,380
Though Ms. Duo has a bad temper,

404
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:32,460
whenever I was neglected and mistreated,

405
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:34,620
she was always the one
who stood up for me.

406
00:17:37,340 --> 00:17:39,780
Your Highness, it is time for your meal.

407
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:47,220
Ms. Hua, what is going on?

408
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,100
Your Highness,

409
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:50,980
the kite is stuck on the roof eaves.

410
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:53,260
Is it broken?

411
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:54,660
Can it still be retrieved?

412
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:55,880
Don't worry, Your Highness.

413
00:17:55,930 --> 00:17:57,420
I'll have someone bring a ladder.

414
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:13,500
Princess Fuqing.

415
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:14,980
Miss Jiang.

416
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:18,020
Your Highness,
the kite is on the rooftop.

417
00:18:18,660 --> 00:18:19,580
Yes.

418
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:21,620
I'll try to knock it down.

419
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:22,900
That'd be great.

420
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:24,500
But Ms. Hua said

421
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:26,140
it was stuck quite high up.

422
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:27,620
Can you reach it?

423
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:28,820
It is quite high.

424
00:18:29,460 --> 00:18:30,380
Let me give it a try.

425
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:49,660
Here it is.

426
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,420
I got it. Take a look.

427
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:56,700
Is it broken?

428
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:58,060
No, it's perfectly fine.

429
00:18:58,820 --> 00:19:00,220
But the string snapped.

430
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:01,700
Your Highness, hold it.

431
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:02,980
I'll just tie

432
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:04,100
the string back.

433
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:06,900
Is it reattached?

434
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,300
Yes.

435
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:09,580
That's good.

436
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:12,660
If only everything in this world

437
00:19:12,780 --> 00:19:14,340
could be mended as easily

438
00:19:14,340 --> 00:19:15,900
as a broken kite string.

439
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:24,060
What do you think of the four candidates

440
00:19:24,780 --> 00:19:25,860
Yu Jin recommended?

441
00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:27,100
Your Majesty,

442
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:29,660
Captain Xie of Lingshui
has an excellent reputation.

443
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:32,020
His annual evaluations
at the Civil Affairs

444
00:19:32,180 --> 00:19:33,540
are consistently top-tier.

445
00:19:33,740 --> 00:19:34,980
However, I believe

446
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,020
there is one concern.

447
00:19:37,740 --> 00:19:38,660
What concern?

448
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:42,460
I heard that Captain Xie
intends to marry

449
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:43,940
the eldest daughter of Earl Dongping.

450
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:46,740
If that happens, he'd become

451
00:19:46,740 --> 00:19:48,180
Prince Yan's brother-in-law.

452
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:51,300
Would that not appear as favoritism?

453
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:54,820
Calling you inflexible
is no exaggeration.

454
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,100
Favoritism applies

455
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:58,590
to the unworthy and incompetent.

456
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,360
When it comes to true talent,

457
00:20:00,380 --> 00:20:03,140
it'd be appointing the worthy,
regardless of ties.

458
00:20:04,020 --> 00:20:04,940
Your Majesty,

459
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,620
Prince Yan

460
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:08,540
became the Commandant

461
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:09,940
of Capital Security

462
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:11,820
through the Tournament.

463
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:14,340
It was accepted by the people.

464
00:20:14,460 --> 00:20:15,380
So, I believe

465
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:16,940
Capital Security is different

466
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:18,160
from other government offices.

467
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:20,100
It's vital to the peace of Ling'an

468
00:20:20,100 --> 00:20:21,540
and the confidence of the people...

469
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:22,460
Enough, enough.

470
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,140
I summoned you here

471
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:26,380
not to listen to a lecture.

472
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:30,100
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

473
00:20:30,620 --> 00:20:31,540
May I ask

474
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:33,140
why you have summoned me?

475
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:36,220
Zhen,

476
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,620
look.

477
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:39,340
Who is that flying the kite?

478
00:20:43,060 --> 00:20:45,660
Are you referring to Miss Jiang Si?

479
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:48,060
Not Jiang Si.

480
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,900
The one standing beside her.

481
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:03,460
Princess Fuqing.

482
00:21:04,860 --> 00:21:05,780
Zhen,

483
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:08,980
I appointed you as her mentor

484
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:10,980
some time ago.

485
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:12,900
What do you think of her?

486
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:16,460
Thanks to your trust,

487
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:19,540
I've had the honor
of teaching Princess Fuqing.

488
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:21,860
She is intelligent, quick-witted,

489
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:23,180
and eager to learn.

490
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,620
And?

491
00:21:26,860 --> 00:21:28,340
She grasps key concepts

492
00:21:28,620 --> 00:21:29,580
of the classics

493
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:31,100
effortlessly

494
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,840
and can even infer beyond the material,

495
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,380
offering insightful perspectives.

496
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:35,900
I am truly impressed.

497
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:37,260
Think again.

498
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:38,740
Beyond her studies,

499
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:40,380
what else have you observed?

500
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:47,460
Indeed.

501
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:50,180
Though born into nobility,

502
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,340
the Princess is humble
and unpretentious.

503
00:21:52,820 --> 00:21:53,860
She treats the servants

504
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:55,180
with kindness and generosity,

505
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:56,860
displaying great compassion.

506
00:21:57,020 --> 00:21:57,940
That's all?

507
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:00,500
Yes.

508
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:11,140
The kite is flying now.

509
00:22:14,100 --> 00:22:15,020
It's up in the air.

510
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:17,180
- Slow down.
- Princess Fuqing.

511
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:19,700
Are you okay?

512
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:20,620
I'm fine.

513
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:31,900
Your Majesty,
sorry for my lapse in composure.

514
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:39,420
Fuqing is my most beloved daughter,

515
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:41,660
and the kindest

516
00:22:41,980 --> 00:22:44,100
and most gracious Princess
in the Palace.

517
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:46,860
I've long wished to find her

518
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:48,580
an upright and reliable husband.

519
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:50,180
Zhen,

520
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:52,980
what do you think of this?

521
00:22:56,460 --> 00:22:57,380
Your Majesty,

522
00:22:58,100 --> 00:23:00,420
I have not yet considered

523
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:01,340
a suitable candidate.

524
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:03,520
I will certainly keep an eye out.

525
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:07,980
You are truly a block of wood.

526
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:09,900
I'm asking

527
00:23:10,540 --> 00:23:14,580
what you think of Fuqing yourself.

528
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:28,700
Your Majesty,

529
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,780
the Princess is of noble birth,

530
00:23:31,260 --> 00:23:33,220
while I am merely a scholar.

531
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,220
I dare not think that way.

532
00:23:35,900 --> 00:23:36,860
So,

533
00:23:38,380 --> 00:23:40,100
you do not wish to marry Fuqing?

534
00:23:41,660 --> 00:23:44,300
I have always regarded Princess Fuqing

535
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:45,540
as my student,

536
00:23:47,740 --> 00:23:48,660
nothing more.

537
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:09,060
Mr. Zhen refused?

538
00:24:09,540 --> 00:24:10,460
I don't believe it.

539
00:24:10,860 --> 00:24:11,780
Why would I lie to you?

540
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,640
I heard it in the Imperial Garden.

541
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:15,140
Our Princess is so wonderful.

542
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:16,580
Whoever marries her

543
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:17,670
would be truly blessed.

544
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,080
Everyone says that Mr. Zhen

545
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:20,640
has an unmatched ability to solve cases,

546
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,620
but in my opinion,

547
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:23,940
he is completely blind.

548
00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:25,780
Princess Fuqing is kind

549
00:24:25,780 --> 00:24:26,700
and gentle.

550
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:28,340
Besides, she is a lineal Princess.

551
00:24:28,580 --> 00:24:29,200
Logically,

552
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,240
suitors lining up for her

553
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:32,280
should be from Changning Palace
to Zhengyang Gate.

554
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:33,500
What are you saying?

555
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:35,140
Ms. Duo.

556
00:24:36,820 --> 00:24:37,740
Please forgive us.

557
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:40,180
How dare you gossip

558
00:24:40,340 --> 00:24:41,540
behind the Princess's back?

559
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,700
Ms. Duo, please forgive us.

560
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:44,780
(Ms. Duo)

561
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:45,700
Your Highness,

562
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,160
this is my failure in discipline.

563
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,460
- They spoke
- Please...

564
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:49,580
- out of turn.
- Have mercy.

565
00:24:49,580 --> 00:24:51,220
They should have their tongues cut out.

566
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:52,460
We won't do it again.

567
00:24:52,460 --> 00:24:53,800
Your Highness, please have mercy.

568
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:56,420
The Empress has always ruled
the harem with kindness

569
00:24:56,780 --> 00:24:58,020
and dislikes harsh punishments.

570
00:24:58,620 --> 00:24:59,580
I think

571
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,560
docking a month's wages
should be enough

572
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:02,820
to teach them a lesson.

573
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:03,780
Absolutely not.

574
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:04,880
If such a light punishment

575
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:06,340
is given,

576
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,500
everyone in Changning Palace

577
00:25:07,500 --> 00:25:08,820
will gossip about their masters.

578
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:09,680
There won't be order.

579
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:11,480
They weren't exactly
speaking out of turn.

580
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:12,780
What's there to punish?

581
00:25:13,060 --> 00:25:13,980
Your Highness...

582
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:15,140
You may leave.

583
00:25:16,060 --> 00:25:17,420
- Thanks.
- Thanks, Your Highness.

584
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:25,860
Your Highness,

585
00:25:26,540 --> 00:25:27,900
don't take

586
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:29,940
what they said to heart.

587
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:31,580
I don't blame them.

588
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,540
Mr. Zhen isn't wrong either.

589
00:25:34,060 --> 00:25:35,260
After all, who would truly love

590
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,580
someone who cannot see?

591
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:38,980
