592
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:41,860
I only wish to stay by Mother's side.

593
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:43,460
Your Highness, have you considered

594
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:45,340
perhaps Mr. Zhen

595
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:48,500
does not mind your blindness at all?

596
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:50,380
Perhaps it is you

597
00:25:51,780 --> 00:25:53,300
who minds it too much,

598
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:55,260
and over time,

599
00:25:55,980 --> 00:25:57,340
it has become a knot in your heart.

600
00:25:57,820 --> 00:25:59,020
You are right.

601
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:01,180
It is my burden.

602
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:03,900
When I speak to others,

603
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:05,900
I cannot see their eyes.

604
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:07,540
So, how can I ever tell

605
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:08,940
if they are sincere?

606
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:12,020
Maybe one day,

607
00:26:12,660 --> 00:26:14,100
your eyes will be healed.

608
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,580
Then

609
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,740
you can see Mr. Zhen for yourself

610
00:26:18,180 --> 00:26:19,180
and ask him about it.

611
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:25,500
Miss Jiang,

612
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,460
can you describe

613
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:28,660
the sky

614
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:29,820
for me?

615
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:36,220
Today's sunset is especially beautiful.

616
00:26:37,060 --> 00:26:39,580
It's deep red, like a glowing sphere,

617
00:26:40,260 --> 00:26:42,980
slowly sinking lower and lower.

618
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:45,140
The clouds at the horizon

619
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:48,220
are streaked with orange and pink.

620
00:26:57,340 --> 00:26:58,500
I can imagine

621
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:00,500
that living

622
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,740
in darkness

623
00:27:03,740 --> 00:27:05,060
must be lonely.

624
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,260
Miss Jiang Si,

625
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:10,020
life in the Palace is lonely.

626
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:12,100
Other than Mother,

627
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:14,260
I have no one to confide in.

628
00:27:14,860 --> 00:27:16,740
No one has ever said

629
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:18,420
what you said today to me before.

630
00:27:20,700 --> 00:27:21,620
Don't worry.

631
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:23,500
We'll have endless things to talk about.

632
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:25,420
Look.

633
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:27,140
I have an older brother and sister,

634
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:28,940
but I don't have a younger sister.

635
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,500
Since you are Prince Yan's sister,

636
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:32,300
you are naturally my sister as well.

637
00:27:33,140 --> 00:27:35,140
I'll visit the Palace often
to keep you company.

638
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:36,740
We'll share many more secrets.

639
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:41,740
(Peace and Prosperity)

640
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,540
