641
00:27:49,460 --> 00:27:51,740
Aunt, I didn't see anything.

642
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,580
I didn't see anything, Aunt.

643
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:55,660
I didn't see anything.

644
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,060
I didn't see anything!

645
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:58,140
Your Highness.

646
00:28:00,060 --> 00:28:01,060
It's me, Jiang.

647
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:02,340
Don't be afraid.

648
00:28:02,620 --> 00:28:03,640
Did you have a nightmare?

649
00:28:04,380 --> 00:28:05,300
Don't be afraid.

650
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:06,900
I'm here.

651
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,220
I heard you saying,

652
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:10,660
"I didn't see anything."

653
00:28:11,700 --> 00:28:12,660
No...

654
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,260
What could frighten you so much?

655
00:28:15,380 --> 00:28:17,100
Is it related to the Grand Princess?

656
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:19,060
I told you I didn't see anything.

657
00:28:19,060 --> 00:28:20,380
Don't ask me.

658
00:28:22,900 --> 00:28:24,300
I saw nothing.

659
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:26,660
I cannot say.

660
00:28:28,500 --> 00:28:30,780
Alright, don't be afraid, Fuqing.

661
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:32,700
Rest assured.

662
00:28:34,020 --> 00:28:35,700
We will do our best

663
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,740
to find a way to heal your eyes.

664
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:41,620
Don't be afraid.

665
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:43,140
Don't be afraid.

666
00:28:43,740 --> 00:28:44,660
I'm here.

667
00:28:45,340 --> 00:28:46,260
I'm here.

668
00:28:58,620 --> 00:29:00,380
Why prepare so much food?

669
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:01,740
I'm in Changning Palace.

670
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:02,940
How could I possibly go hungry?

671
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:04,980
I haven't been by your side

672
00:29:04,980 --> 00:29:06,260
these past few days.

673
00:29:06,780 --> 00:29:08,900
What if you lost your appetite?

674
00:29:10,700 --> 00:29:12,420
So? Any progress?

675
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:15,300
Based on the Empress's attitude

676
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,480
toward the Grand Princess

677
00:29:16,760 --> 00:29:18,460
these days,

678
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:19,620
I'm sure

679
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:21,620
their relationship is strained.

680
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:23,740
In fact, the Empress

681
00:29:23,740 --> 00:29:25,100
seems to fear the Grand Princess.

682
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:28,340
She has poor relations

683
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,740
with many consorts in the harem.

684
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:32,500
Supporting the Empress

685
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,780
doesn't necessarily mean anything.

686
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:36,920
Perhaps she just finds her
easier to use.

687
00:29:38,700 --> 00:29:40,660
Empress Di has no sons,

688
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:42,140
her family holds no power,

689
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:43,460
and in the past,

690
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:45,220
she never received much favor.

691
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:47,780
To the Grand Princess,

692
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:49,620
these weaknesses might be seen

693
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,300
as advantages.

694
00:29:52,660 --> 00:29:54,260
These advantages make her

695
00:29:54,420 --> 00:29:55,580
easier to control.

696
00:29:57,060 --> 00:29:57,980
By the way,

697
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:58,820
last night,

698
00:29:58,820 --> 00:30:00,100
Princess Fuqing had a nightmare.

699
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:01,820
She kept calling out for her aunt

700
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:02,980
in her sleep,

701
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:04,490
saying she didn't

702
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:06,380
see anything.

703
00:30:07,580 --> 00:30:09,500
The more she insisted she saw nothing,

704
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,620
the more likely it was
that she saw a secret.

705
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:13,540
I suspect

706
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:15,420
it must be something truly terrifying,

707
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:17,940
so she's been afraid to speak of it,

708
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:19,940
fearing that the Grand Princess
will retaliate

709
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:21,020
and harm Empress Di.

710
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:25,220
Do you think her blindness

711
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:27,740
is connected to this?

712
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:31,460
If the Grand Princess

713
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,940
has spies from Nanwu

714
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,340
hidden in Changning Palace,

715
00:30:34,580 --> 00:30:35,500
then this person

716
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:37,700
could both gather intelligence

717
00:30:38,540 --> 00:30:39,820
and keep an eye on Fuqing,

718
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:42,140
preventing her
from revealing the secret.

719
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:46,260
Should we tell the Empress

720
00:30:46,700 --> 00:30:47,620
about this?

721
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:49,900
Would she

722
00:30:50,100 --> 00:30:51,300
make Fuqing confess?

723
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:54,860
Fuqing has kept this
from the Empress for years.

724
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:56,380
She must be

725
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:57,740
suffering immensely.

726
00:30:58,260 --> 00:31:00,380
We can't reveal this

727
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:02,500
without her permission.

728
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:03,740
Yes.

729
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:05,020
Right now,

730
00:31:05,580 --> 00:31:06,620
our top priority

731
00:31:06,860 --> 00:31:07,980
is finding the spy

732
00:31:07,980 --> 00:31:09,100
in Changning Palace.

733
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:10,740
We cannot let them continue

734
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:11,840
to wreak havoc in the harem.

735
00:31:13,380 --> 00:31:14,260
But there are

736
00:31:14,260 --> 00:31:15,780
so many maids here.

737
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:18,520
We'll have to check the palace registry.

738
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:19,780
From my observations,

739
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:22,300
two people seem suspicious.

740
00:31:22,420 --> 00:31:23,300
Who?

741
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,380
One is Ms. Duo;

742
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,620
the other is Ms. Hua.

743
00:31:25,860 --> 00:31:26,940
They spoke

744
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:27,820
out of turn.

745
00:31:27,820 --> 00:31:29,420
They should have their tongues cut out.

746
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:31,760
The Empress has always ruled
the harem with kindness

747
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:32,980
and dislikes harsh punishments.

748
00:31:32,980 --> 00:31:33,980
Ms. Duo's family

749
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:35,660
once ran a martial arts school.

750
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:37,140
She knows some combat skills,

751
00:31:37,580 --> 00:31:38,540
rarely smiles,

752
00:31:38,780 --> 00:31:40,020
and is highly decisive.

753
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:41,980
When handling maids,

754
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:43,020
she is utterly ruthless.

755
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:45,460
Ms. Hua is an orphan.

756
00:31:45,700 --> 00:31:46,660
She is always warm

757
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:47,980
and cheerful

758
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:49,540
and never argues with anyone.

759
00:31:51,580 --> 00:31:53,060
But she is only

760
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:54,700
in charge of daily affairs,

761
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:56,720
so she has no reason
to leave the Palace.

762
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:58,180
Ms. Duo, however,

763
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,820
works for the Empress

764
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,760
and has many opportunities
to go outside.

765
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:03,380
Not leaving the Palace

766
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:05,400
doesn't mean she has no way
to send messages.

767
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,500
Carrier pigeons could be used.

768
00:32:08,820 --> 00:32:09,740
Carrier pigeons?

769
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,340
I noticed scratches

770
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,700
on Ms. Hua's fingers,

771
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:24,220
the kind left by pigeon claws.

772
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:25,280
That matches up perfectly.

773
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:26,540
Could Ms. Hua

774
00:32:27,340 --> 00:32:28,620
really be the spy?

775
00:32:29,660 --> 00:32:30,580
We must act quickly.

776
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:32,660
Let's inform the Empress at once.

777
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:35,500
You also want to learn etiquette?

778
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:36,940
Yes.

779
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:39,460
Jiang Si's father is an Earl.

780
00:32:39,460 --> 00:32:41,340
Her manners are far better than mine.

781
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:44,300
If she performs flawlessly
at the wedding

782
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:45,620
while I make a mistake,

783
00:32:45,620 --> 00:32:47,260
it would be utterly humiliating.

784
00:32:47,380 --> 00:32:48,580
But I can't stay

785
00:32:48,580 --> 00:32:50,100
in the Palace to study,

786
00:32:50,260 --> 00:32:51,860
so I wanted to borrow

787
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:53,020
Ms. Hua for a while.

788
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:54,620
Ms. Hua?

789
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:56,540
What are you two up to?

790
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:57,940
I just want

791
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,340
to learn proper etiquette.

792
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:03,100
Fine then.

793
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:07,140
Your Highness, I don't want to go.

794
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:09,700
But Prince Yan asked for you.

795
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:11,620
- Your Highness...
- Go pack.

796
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:17,380
Yes.

797
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,120
Thank you, Your Highness.

798
00:33:27,340 --> 00:33:28,260
Prince Yan,

799
00:33:29,580 --> 00:33:30,700
can I trust

800
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:31,900
you and Jiang Si?

801
00:33:32,260 --> 00:33:33,180
After my return,

802
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,300
you are the only one in the Palace

803
00:33:35,910 --> 00:33:36,940
who has treated me kindly.

804
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:40,460
You're a good child,

805
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:42,660
and so is Jiang Si.

806
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:49,700
(Prince Yan's Mansion)

807
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:57,660
Ms. Hua,

808
00:33:58,380 --> 00:33:59,580
we've arrived. Come out.

809
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,940
You refused to leave the Palace,

810
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:04,660
but we're at the doorstep now.

811
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:06,460
There's no need to hide
in the sedan chair.

812
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:21,340
Your Highness, you misunderstand.

813
00:34:21,820 --> 00:34:22,980
I am not unwilling.

814
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:25,380
Since I entered the Palace at 13,

815
00:34:25,660 --> 00:34:27,900
I have never stepped outside.

816
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,340
Everything out there has changed.

817
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:32,620
The outside world is

818
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:34,540
