819
00:34:34,860 --> 00:34:36,220
Is that what troubles you?

820
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:38,780
Yes, you wouldn't understand.

821
00:34:40,220 --> 00:34:41,540
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

822
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:45,740
Wait.

823
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,820
The flowers in your mansion

824
00:34:48,180 --> 00:34:49,340
are common in my hometown.

825
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:52,180
Seeing them again feels so familiar.

826
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:54,220
It seems you and Lingshui

827
00:34:54,220 --> 00:34:55,260
are truly connected.

828
00:34:55,260 --> 00:34:56,180
Where?

829
00:34:56,300 --> 00:34:57,220
Lingshui?

830
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:10,980
Miss Jiang.

831
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:13,180
It's you.

832
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:14,500
Did you plant the Mang Worm

833
00:35:14,500 --> 00:35:15,560
in Princess Fuqing's eyes?

834
00:35:15,860 --> 00:35:16,780
It was me.

835
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:19,020
How does a noble lady of Dazhou like you

836
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:20,580
know so much about Mang Worms

837
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,580
from Nanwu?

838
00:35:21,580 --> 00:35:22,740
How did you find out?

839
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,460
In that case,

840
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:31,580
Miss Jiang,

841
00:35:31,580 --> 00:35:32,980
you've known too much.

842
00:35:33,660 --> 00:35:35,140
I'm afraid I must do this.

843
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:44,620
(Peace and Prosperity)

844
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:50,950
Where is Miss Jiang?

845
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,660
She is in the back garden with Ms. Duo.

846
00:36:00,140 --> 00:36:01,500
Let go of me. I'm fine.

847
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:02,500
She is a Nanwu woman.

848
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,870
She can save Princess Fuqing.

849
00:36:08,210 --> 00:36:09,440
Though she's a Nanwu woman,

850
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,500
I have confirmed

851
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:11,620
that she planted

852
00:36:11,620 --> 00:36:12,660
the gu worm

853
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,860
in the Princess's eyes.

854
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,500
So, she knows how to cure it.

855
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,420
Tell me how.

856
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:20,580
I'm just clearing obstacles

857
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:21,500
for the Grand Princess.

858
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,540
Ms. Duo,

859
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:23,780
I'm the Saintess.

860
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:25,220
Will you serve me

861
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:26,580
or the Grand Princess?

862
00:36:27,020 --> 00:36:27,940
You choose.

863
00:36:47,420 --> 00:36:48,380
Greetings, Saintess.

864
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:49,780
